Web Analysis
Yes
No
Analytic cookies help us better understand how users like you, like to use Machineseeker.co.uk.                    This means that we can optimize our website, apps and communication and remain interesting and relevant.                    Your consent covers all sites of the Machineseeker Group and includes the processing of data outside the European Economic Area, where there may not be a comparable level of data protection, e.g. in the USA.
Marketing
Yes
No
Machineseeker.co.uk and our partners also use third-party cookies.                    These cookies are used to display personalized advertising on other websites.                    This advertising is based on your browsing behavior, for example the listings you have seen.                    This way you get more relevant advertising.
